headline: International Paper Celebrates the Groundbreaking of Greenfield Packaging Facility in Waterloo, Iowa
summary: International Paper (NYSE: IP; LSE: IPC), a global leader in sustainable packaging, is proud to announce the groundbreaking of its new state-of-the-art sustainable, packaging box plant in Waterloo, Iowa.
